1
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,280
Is this

2
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,200
for me?

3
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:57,000
Her phone is still here.

4
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:18,560
Hello?

5
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:23,599
Mao Liang?

6
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:24,960
Why isn't she answering?

7
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,280
Jiang Yue isn't here.

8
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:27,840
Who are you?

9
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,280
You don't know me?

10
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,879
When she comes back,

11
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,280
I'll tell her to call you.

12
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:36,719
Hello?

13
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,400
Hello.

14
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:56,919
Li Si.

15
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:58,599
Boss.

16
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,159
Where's Jiang Yue?

17
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,560
I don't know.

18
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:05,280
Didn't I tell you to keep an eye on her?

19
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,120
But last night,

20
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,599
you were badly hurt.

21
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:09,800
We were busy taking care of you,

22
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:11,439
and didn't notice where she went.

23
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,800
What about the people patrolling outside?

24
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,719
They didn't notice Jiang Yue either.

25
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,439
A truck passed by

26
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,240
but we don't know where it came from.

27
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,479
It's weird.

28
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:31,000
Miss Jiang's scent is still here,

29
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,840
but there's no scent of the driver.

30
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,599
He's good at hiding his scent.

31
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,439
If I'm right,

32
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:37,639
the driver

33
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,439
is a bounty hunter.

34
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,000
You go back first.

35
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,680
I'll go find him.

36
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,479
After all these years,

37
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,520
you still only care about that woman.

38
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,919
She's not Li Feiyuan.

39
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,919
How could I forget that face?

40
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,680
She killed our parents

41
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,840
and almost killed you.

42
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,000
Tell me,

43
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,120
where is she?

44
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:18,279
She and her car fell into the sea,

45
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,160
just like what I did back then,

46
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,079
leaving no trace.

47
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:29,439
The Li Residence has been burned to ashes.

48
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,360
It's a pity that Li Feiyuan

49
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,600
disappeared.

50
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,920
I couldn't tear her apart with my own hands.

51
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:36,079
Che...

52
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,240
Enough.

53
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,720
I helped you take revenge.

54
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,120
You don't appreciate me.

55
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,319
The soldiers are looking for the murderer.

56
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,079
The wanted order of Hidden Edge is posted on the city gate.

57
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,920
Stupid human.

58
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:57,279
They still think it's the ungrateful guard.

59
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,040
Poor my brother.

60
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:01,000
He wants to beg them for mercy,

61
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,759
but have nowhere to go.

62
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:04,240
I have nothing to do

63
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,519
with the Li Residence.

64
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,680
Very well.

65
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,480
You have been domesticated for so long,

66
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,360
and it's time for you to experience

67
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,360
the taste of being a stray like me.

68
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,319
One day,

69
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,079
we will meet again.

70
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:24,079
Even if you hate me,

71
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,160
I can't just stand by and do nothing.

72
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:29,480
I never hated you.

73
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,759
The servants and women and children had all escaped.

74
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:34,920
Che,

75
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:38,040
you are a man of justice,

76
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,560
and never killed innocent people.

77
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:46,480
You covered up her scent.

78
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:49,240
Tell me,

79
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,120
where

80
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:53,160
is she?

81
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,279
Too late.

82
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,920
I can let her live,

83
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:06,199
but I won't let a woman with such a face

84
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:07,800
appear by your side.

85
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,399
It just so happens

86
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,959
that someone wanted her dead.

87
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,920
I merely played along

88
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,480
and did them a favor.

89
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:15,920
Who?

90
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:18,839
I don't know.

91
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:19,959
I don't care.

92
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,639
She's been delivered to the arena.

93
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:24,319
It's up to them how they deal with her.

94
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,079
The arena is packed with people.

95
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,720
How could you possibly take them all?

96
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,480
What if your cover is blown?

97
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,839
The cargo ship was intercepted again.

98
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,240
Lu sent someone to guard the port.

99
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:45,000
No wonder Mr. Qin is so angry.

100
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,519
If we don't deliver the goods, we'll be in trouble.

101
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,560
It must be illegal.

102
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,120
We meet again.

103
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,480
You offered a huge reward for me.

104
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,240
Now you're finally in my hands.

105
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:03,199
Wildcat.

106
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:07,079
I thought it was some big shot.

107
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:12,079
The employer won't show up easily.

108
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:14,519
To us,

109
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:17,839
just a number to us.

110
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,680
If I kill you,

111
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,800
I can deliver the goods,

112
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,199
get paid,

113
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,839
and get back at you for beating me up.

114
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,279
If you kill me,

115
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,319
you may not

116
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,000
get paid,

117
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:36,079
and you might lose your job.

118
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,959
Which is more important to your boss,

119
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,800
Qin Yeren,

120
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,120
catching Lu Zhiyu's woman

121
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:46,920
to your boss Qin Yeren?

122
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,759
You mean...

123
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:50,600
If I were you,

124
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,759
I would report

125
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,160
a big catch

126
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,399
instead of being a fool

127
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:58,639
and missing a great chance for promotion.

128
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:04,399
Go!

129
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,399
Go!

130
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:06,519
Hit him!

131
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,480
Hit him!

132
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,959
Come on, hit him!

133
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,199
Hit him!

134
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:11,759
Go!

135
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,560
Hit him!

136
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,120
Hurry up!

137
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:15,120
Come on!

138
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,519
Beat him!

139
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,720
Hold him down!

140
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,480
Hit him!

141
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,519
Hit him!

142
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,240
Enough!

143
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:24,000
What are you doing?

144
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,959
You don't need to come tomorrow.

145
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,000
I've known Lu for a long time.

146
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:48,399
He only has a few brothers around him.

147
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,799
I really don't know

148
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,840
he has a relationship with a woman.

149
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,759
It's just a relationship.

150
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:57,120
There's no need for the whole world to know, right?

151
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,519
He has seen us together.

152
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,039
Mr. Qin is a smart man.

153
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,879
How about we make a deal?

154
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:06,919
You tell me who is offering a reward for me.

155
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:09,960
I'll pay double the price for his information.

156
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,799
Reward?

157
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,840
These are all done in secret.

158
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:17,919
The identity of the employer

159
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:20,080
is only known to the devil.

160
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,840
I'm not interested.

161
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,080
It doesn't matter.

162
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:26,240
Then let's make another deal.

163
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,360
Do you have any chips?

164
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,840
Port passage right.

165
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:40,399
Are you interested?

166
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:44,679
Lu Zhiyu's men are all on the dock.

167
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,360
As long as I say a word,

168
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,200
they will let you go immediately.

169
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,519
Who knows if you'll

170
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:54,080
let them go

171
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,080
or call for help?

172
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,320
You can put someone to follow me.

173
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,799
If I don't do as you say,

174
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:03,720
you can kill me.

175
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:09,159
If it works out,

176
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,799
I'll give you freedom.

177
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:19,639
Deal.

178
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,759
Jiang Yue,

179
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:51,080
compared to Lu,

180
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,679
you're

181
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,000
than Lu.

182
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:04,960
Watch out!

183
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,279
Mr. Lu,

184
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:30,000
long time no see.

185
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,399
Qin Yeren,

186
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,039
you've learned nothing from the past.

187
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,559
Or are you relying on someone's power

188
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:37,080
to make a move?

189
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,879
Only a dog

190
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:43,360
would rely on someone's power.

191
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:46,000
In business,

192
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,720
connections are everything.

193
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:50,000
Just like Miss Jiang beside you,

194
00:11:50,639 --> 00:11:52,679
she's here to discuss business with me.

195
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,799
Just now,

196
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:56,879
she tried to betray you to gain my trust.

197
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,639
Sowing discord.

198
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:01,080
Don't believe him.

199
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:02,279
Are you hurt?

200
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:04,600
Okay.

201
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:05,519
Go home.

202
00:12:18,799 --> 00:12:19,440
I'll stay.

203
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:21,080
She goes first.

204
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:22,480
No way.

205
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,480
Let's go together.

206
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:24,919
You are so bold.

207
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,200
Really bold.

208
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,720
You two together,

209
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,519
barehanded,

210
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,399
on my turf.

211
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,799
Are you trying to be tough?

212
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:36,080
Who's talking tough?

213
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,720
Let me see.

214
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,279
You look good.

215
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:06,240
You passed.

216
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,720
Xiaoya,

217
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,240
this is not your business.

218
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:11,720
What?

219
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:14,200
Aren't you supposed to find me a bodyguard?

220
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,759
Those guys are not good enough.

221
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:19,360
He's the only one.

222
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:21,600
What?

223
00:13:21,919 --> 00:13:23,159
You're not here to apply?

224
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,440
Of course not.

225
00:13:25,399 --> 00:13:26,720
I'm so handsome. Can't you see?

226
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,080
Who are you?

227
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:31,039
I don't need a female bodyguard.

228
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,279
You...

229
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:37,840
You...

230
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:39,919
Defeat them all,

231
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:42,200
and I'll let you go.

232
00:13:46,519 --> 00:13:47,840
[He can't be exposed.]

233
00:14:11,559 --> 00:14:12,759
A bunch of useless people.

234
00:14:13,799 --> 00:14:15,399
No need to waste time.

235
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,080
Mr. Qin,

236
00:14:17,519 --> 00:14:19,240
pick some real fighters next time.

237
00:14:29,759 --> 00:14:30,600
You're not honorable.

238
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:33,440
Let go of me.

239
00:14:36,399 --> 00:14:37,320
Don't hit the face.

240
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,720
He's mine.

241
00:14:39,279 --> 00:14:40,120
Dream on!
